originalText.text: I have not seen Mr. Friedlander since 2005, when we briefly worked together. He was a nurse at that time.  I have not personally treated Mr. Friedlander for any psychiatric illness at FEGS or at my subsequent position. I now work as a writer, and am currently writing a memoir detailing my days working with Mr. Friedlander and so many at St. Vincent's, prior to it's closure. I certainly wish him all the best and hope for a speedy recovery.
